                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>*@
                </li>
                <li>
                    If it was balanced last Bank Statement please state the date and final balance on your register that was used to balance your checkbook and list any transactions that have not yet cleared on your bank statement.
                    <br />
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label class="control-label col-sm-2" for="email">Final balance:</label>
                        <div class="col-sm-2">
                            <input type="number" class="form-control" id="email" name="email">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label class="control-label col-sm-2" for="mail">Date:</label>
                        <div class="col-sm-2">
                            <input type="text" class="form-control" id="mail" name="mail">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <br />
                    <br />

                    Outstanding Transactions that have not yet cleared
                    <br />
                    <br />
